l\nanomalies and the heat-flux variation is large, the core will be in a low-$S$\nregime in which the stable layer is likely penetrated by boundary-driven flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Jul 2018 11:01:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 09:59:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
